Like many others, I'm simply trying to make today a bit better than yesterday.

There's a lot of variables that go into this - my faith, family, work, and other interests.

I hope to share milestones or insights I find relevant to my own progress with the hopes that you enjoy or find value in them as well.

I support my wondeful family by advancing state policies that reduce barriers to opportunity and success for others.

In my free time I enjoy a great book (and even some not-so great books), building websites and apps using modern JavaScript, or jumping into an mmo.
